reviewText: My granddaughter and my son in-law both love this movie.  They watch it all the time.  My son in law remembers it from when he was growing up.  THis was a great gift for both of them.
Very nice and funny movie.  I enjoyed watching this at the movies as a child.

Said it was very good. Like new. It was not. Both dics are dirty and scatched up. The cover is torn on the inside and worn on the outside. Bought it as a gift for my bf so I can't check it out to see if it will play all the way  until nov. 13th. I guess it was only 23 bucks but I feel cheated. Should of just spent the money for the brand new one.
